OCF to NI Ratio = Net Cash Flow from Operating Activities / Net Income

## 5. Net Profit Margin
Net Profit Margin = Net Income / Total Revenue * 100%

## 6. Gross Profit Margin

Gross Profit Margin = 2,861,769.51 / 4,879,769.51 * 100% = 58.65%
